@startuml sidecar-architecture
title Istio Sidecar Mode — Arquitetura

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam backgroundColor transparent

package "Control Plane (istio-system)" {
  [istiod] as istiod
}

node "Nó Kubernetes" {
  package "Pod payment-api" {
    [App payment-api] as app1
    [Envoy sidecar\n(istio-proxy)] as sidecar1
    [iptables\n(istio-init, roda 1x no start)] as ipt1
  }
  package "Pod payment-cache" {
    [App payment-cache] as app2
    [Envoy sidecar\n(istio-proxy)] as sidecar2
    [iptables\n(istio-init, roda 1x no start)] as ipt2
  }
}

app1 -down-> ipt1 : tráfego de saída\nredirecionado
ipt1 -down-> sidecar1
sidecar1 -right-> sidecar2 : mTLS (HTTP/2)
sidecar2 -down-> ipt2
ipt2 -down-> app2

istiod ..> sidecar1 : xDS (config, certificados)
istiod ..> sidecar2 : xDS (config, certificados)

note bottom of sidecar1
  1 processo Envoy completo (L4 + L7)
  por Pod — mesmo que o serviço só
  precise de mTLS, ele paga o custo
  de um proxy L7 inteiro.
end note

@enduml
